---
title: Creamy Chive Chicken with Lemony Rice and a Dijon-Apple Salad
description: We’re big fans of pan sauces because they’re an easy way to add tons of restaurant-level flavor to your dish. Here, tangy lemon juice, punchy dijon, sour cream, and fresh chives mingle to create a condiment that truly takes seared chicken to the next level. On the side, there’s zesty lemon rice and a green salad that’s bursting with crispy pieces of apple...because you only deserve the best!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dc047615197ee55a945fc4f-7e914ca3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-chive-chicken-5dc047615197ee55a945fc4f-265ff35f.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-chive-chicken-5dc047615197ee55a945fc4f
servings: 2
author: Michelle Doll Olson
nutrition:
  calories: 640 kcal
  fat: 31 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
  carbohydrates: 52 g
  sugar: 9 g
  protein: 39 g
  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 470 mg
cuisine: North America
course: main course
